 210:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Resets the RCC clock configuration to the default reset state.
 211:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   The default reset state of the clock configuration is given below:
 212:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - HSI ON and used as CPU and system clock source
 213:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - MSI and HSE OFF
 214:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - PLL1, PLL2, PLL3 and PLL4 bypassed
 215:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - AHB, APB Bus prescalers set to 1
 216:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - CSS, MCO1 and MCO2 OFF
 217:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - All interrupts disabled
 218:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   This function doesn't modify the configuration of the
 219:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - Peripheral clocks
 220:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - Memory clocks
 221:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - Misc clocks
 222:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - LSI, LSE and RTC clocks
 223:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - ICx selections and dividers
 224:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @retval HAL status
 225:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc.c ****   */
